{"tid":1226334,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷知識] 警察的起源","createTime":"2019-06-15T11:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:10:18.000Z","uid":133611,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"feb99553c753c244b760a358bd00dec0bc53738e","tid":1226334,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:04:52.000Z","msg":"警察的起源<br />\n文／土撥鼠@破土工作室<br />\n<br />\n摘要：在英國和美國，現代意義上的警察是在短短的三十年內被創造的&mdash;&mdash;從1825年到1855年。這一創造不是為了應對犯罪率的增長，而是為了應對新生工人階級的集體行動，如罷工、暴亂等。直到今天，警察的主要作用還是通過控制集體人口來維持資本主義社會秩序。而他們選擇性地利用法律去處理個人犯罪行為，只是管理集體的策略之一。若要超越警察制的壓迫，可以參考巴黎公社如何試圖實現中世紀「公社」原有的理想：人與人之間平等自治的共同體（self-governing community of equals）。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1033708a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1033708a&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgDMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=52c6cd29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1033708a&h=b9dda5e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1033708a</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9905e09c9b3263b3ac28703cdf2d8dc6dea2ec6","tid":1226334,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec521c339532b03bd4c47b84f19e24eebf2f906c","tid":1226334,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:09:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2638d0b0ec34c1d0477b39ae5cba102f866c7d24","tid":1226334,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779890e0fdbd1a42c2f60acc7f81bc80e32dbe06","tid":1226334,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95214cd0ee3ff323d9ee34ed4e0a075f60e24ac","tid":1226334,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"Push r"},{"pid":"b059dcdf34e3b68834653040849b8c433ea6bb40","tid":1226334,"uid":65912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:33:33.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"3f70d01e644e52589681531369ee0c4cb342a1bf","tid":1226334,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"【社會課】甚麼是警察國家？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204609</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}